    div#content
      h1 Worth PoE
      p 
        | This is a website to check what is the most profitable choice in a given situation (e.g. Apex of Ascension), or the less expensive (e.g. a challenge).
        | Prices are fetched from 
        a(href='https://poe.ninja/') poe.ninja
        |  every #{fetchInterval / (60 * 1000)} minutes.
        | This website isn't affiliated with either poe.ninja nor GGG.
        | If you want to report a bug/error, or request a feature I invite you to 
        a(href='https://github.com/FrancoisMentec/worth-poe/issues/new') submit a new issue
        |  on GitHub (make sure a similar issue haven't been submitted yet).
      
